    "Id": "vehicledef_Trask_2",
    "Name": "Trask TSK-02",
    "Details": "Developed by Rileys Rangers as an in house attack helicopter, the Trask proved successful enough that large quantities were sold to the Cannopian armed forces and other mercenary groups. A 30 ton VTOL, the Trask can reach speeds of 160kph, thanks to its 160 rated XL engine; while 5 tons of heavy ferro-fibrous armor provide heavy protection. The Trask TSK-02 is armed Streak SRM-6 and dedicates the rest of its tonnage to a 5 ton infantry bay with 2.5 tons of additional cargo space.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar biomes.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 10/15 hexes / 300/450 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Heavy Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       150     15\n<b>Left</b>         120     15\n<b>Right</b>       120     15\n<b>Rear</b>         95     15\n\n<b>Total</b>      500     75</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Medium</color>\n\n<color=#ffcc00> Can carry 1 Battle Armor Squads.</color>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_traskattackhelicopter"
  },
